<div metal:fill-slot="main">

   <h1>Welcome to Extropy</h1>

   <div class="documentDescription">The <a href="http://plonesolutions.com/">Plone Solutions</a> project management,  getting-stuff-done and distributed coordination tool</div>

   
   
   <p>Extropy uses a hierarical structure to organise its content<p>
   
   <ul>
       <li>
           Project
           <ul>
               <li>
                Package
                   <ul>
                       <li>
                            Activity
                       </li>
                       <li>
                            Deliverable
                            <ul>
                                <li>
                                    Task
                                </li>
                            </ul>
                       </li>
                   </ul>

               </li>
           </ul>
       </li>
   </ul>

   <dl>
        <dt>Project</dt>
        <dd>A project we work on, commonly a defined piece of work for a customer, with a defined start, end and budget</dd>
    
    
        <dt>Package</dt>
        <dd>A defined part of a project, usually delimited either by time or by theme/topic</dd>

        <dt>Deliverable</dt>
        <dd>A defined "something" to be produced or delievered, usually for a customer</dd>
    

        <dt>Activity</dt>
        <dd>
            Less clearly defined activities in a project. <br/>
            The things that take time, but are not clearly defined<br/>
            Activities do not contain tasks<br/>
            Activities may be billable, and you may register work-hours on them<br/>
            
        </dd>
    

        <dt></dt>
        <dd></dd>
    

        <dt></dt>
        <dd></dd>
    
    
   </dl>



